    "en": {
      "title": "Ranjan, who is serving a prison sentence, watches 'The Game'",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Ranjan Ramanayake, the popular actor who played the lead role in the movie 'The Game' and was imprisoned in Welikada Bandhanagar, had the opportunity to watch the movie at 'Club City Center' today (19).",
        "Jails Media Spokesman, Jails Commissioner Mr. Chandana Ekanayake said that the opportunity was given to Mr. Ramanayake with the approval of the Ministry of Justice as per the request of the director of the movie 'The Game'."
      ],
